ry of the reference stars, and when instrumental\nsignatures are properly removed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jul 2013 18:40:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Jul 2013 16:34:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
