bing the cold clumpy phase of the inter-stellar medium\nin self-consistent simulations of galaxy mergers, albeit so far neglected, is\nimportant to predict the black hole dynamics in galaxy merger remnants.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jul 2013 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Oct 2013 20:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
