ging them to use\nTVWS spectrum through greater spectrum availability (as measured by percentage\nof winning bidders) as well as to the coordinating spectrum manager through\nrevenue generation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 2013 10:42:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Dec 2013 00:50:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-09"}
